@startuml
title 미핏 - 채용공고 URL 수집 시퀀스 (사용자 → Backend → scraping Worker → SQLAlchemy → SSE)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  ActorBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantBorderColor #2196F3
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantFontSize 11
  BoxBorderColor #B0BEC5
  BoxBackgroundColor #ECEFF1
}

actor "사용자" as U
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend\nUserJobDescription\nAPIView" as BE
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "Redis\nscraping 큐" as Q
participant "scraping Worker\n(Celery + Playwright)" as W
boundary "httpx" as HTTP
boundary "Playwright\nBrowser (per worker)" as PW
participant "OpenAI\n(text / Vision)" as LLM
participant "Backend SSE\nUserJobDescription\nScrapingStatus\nConsumer" as SSE

== Step 1. URL 등록 + 태스크 발행 ==

U -> FE : 채용공고 URL 입력
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/user-job-descriptions/\n{ url, title, application_status }
activate BE
  BE -> BE : CreateUserJobDescriptionSerializer 검증
  BE -> BE : CreateUserJobDescriptionService.execute()
  BE -> DB : get_or_create JobDescription\n(collection_status=pending)
  BE -> DB : UserJobDescription 생성
  BE -> Q : send_task("scraping.tasks.scrape_job_posting",\n  args=[jd_id, url], queue="scraping")
  BE --> FE : { uuid, ... }
deactivate BE

== Step 2. SSE 구독 ==

FE -> SSE : GET /sse/user-job-descriptions/{uuid}/collection-status/\nAuthorization: Bearer {JWT}
activate SSE
  SSE -> DB : UserJobDescription 소유권 검증 (user_id 매치)
  SSE --> FE : 200 OK\nContent-Type: text/event-stream
  note right of SSE : 1.5 초 폴링\nDB.collection_status 변화 감지

== Step 3. Worker 처리 시작 ==

Q -> W : pull scrape_job_posting(jd_id, url)
activate W
  W -> DB : UPDATE collection_status = in_progress

== Step 4. Pipeline — Stage 1 (httpx 직접 요청) ==

W -> W : pipeline.run(url, browser)
W -> W : URL 정규화 (사람인 relay → direct)
W -> W : get_plugin(url)\n(jobkorea / jobplanet / default)

W -> HTTP : GET url\n(랜덤 User-Agent + stealth headers)
activate HTTP
  HTTP --> W : HTML or 403/429/503 (bot 차단)
deactivate HTTP

alt HTTP 실패 / bot 차단 / HTML 불완전
  == Step 4-B. Pipeline — Stage 2 (Playwright fallback) ==
  W -> PW : page.goto(url, wait_until=domcontentloaded)
  activate PW
    PW -> PW : 500ms + networkidle
    PW -> PW : Cloudflare JS challenge bypass
    PW -> PW : plugin.before_extract(page)\n(버튼 클릭 / 스크롤)
    PW -> PW : iframe HTML / image 수집
    PW --> W : final HTML + image bytes
  deactivate PW
end

== Step 5. HTML → Text + LLM 추출 분기 ==

W -> W : clean_html_to_text(html)\n(script/style/nav 제거)

alt 텍스트 ≥ 300 자
  W -> LLM : extract_with_llm(text, url)\nModel: gpt-4o-mini
  activate LLM
    LLM --> W : JobPosting JSON\n(title, company, duties, requirements, ...)
  deactivate LLM

  opt duties/preferred 비어있음 + image 존재
    W -> LLM : extract_with_vision_llm(images, url)\nModel: gpt-4o (Vision)
    LLM --> W : 보강 필드
  end

else 텍스트 < 300 자 + image 존재
  W -> LLM : extract_with_vision_llm(images, url)\nModel: gpt-4o (Vision)
  LLM --> W : JobPosting JSON
end

== Step 6. SQLAlchemy 직접 저장 (Worker → Backend DB) ==

W -> DB : UPDATE JobDescription\nSET title, company, duties, requirements, ...,\n  collection_status=done, scraped_at=now()
note right of W
  scraping Worker 가
  backend PostgreSQL 에
  SQLAlchemy 로 직접 write
  (별도 callback task 없음)
end note
deactivate W

== Step 7. SSE 상태 변경 감지 → 클라이언트 push ==

SSE -> DB : SELECT collection_status (1.5s 폴링)
SSE -> FE : event: status\ndata: { collection_status: done, updated_at }
deactivate SSE
FE -> FE : 수집 완료 UI 갱신

U <- FE : 채용공고 상세 페이지 표시

== Step 8. 실패 시 재시도 ==

note over W
  실패 시 Celery 재시도:
  - max_retries=2, retry_delay=120s
  - soft_time_limit=120s, hard=150s
  - 최종 실패 → collection_status=error,
    error_message 기록
end note

footer MeFit - 채용공고 스크래핑 (FR-JD-01~10) — httpx → Playwright → text/Vision LLM
@enduml
